Tribe challenge

The top 5 tribes will split 50k $Lords based on their position on the guild leaderboard

- **1st Place Tribe**: 40% - 20,000 $Lords
- **2nd Place Tribe**: 25% - 12,500 $Lords
- **3rd Place Tribe**: 15% - 7,500 $Lords
- **4th Place Tribe**: 12% - 6,000 $Lords
- **5th Place Tribe**: 8% - 4,000 $Lords

A tribe is any team of 2+ players who have formed a guild in the game client.

To avoid the winning tribe from being joined by new members **you must have joined a tribe by Monday 12:00 UTC** when a snapshot of all teams will be taken.

Creator challenge

10 creators will split 50k $Lords (5k $Lords each).

The challenge:  Tell player and game stories from the world of Eternum over the preseason.

This is a creative competition that will be judged by 3 DAO contributors who's decision is binding.

What the judges will be looking for:

- quality of storytelling,
- how well received it is in the community,
- how it is received in other channels (like X, YouTube etc),
- platform variety (streaming, X, YouTube, TikTok, Instagram - whereever you can reach an audience).

The first 5 creators that can prove they have authentically generated a million non-spam impressions of relevant storytelling content can claim an additional 10k $Lord bounty, each.  This is an award to recognise virality, not to encourage spamming.

To enter tell your stories, then drop links, screenshots and any key information in the Creator Challenge discord channel.

